Installation Instructions
-------------------------

   1. Install all required dependencies:

      * FOX >= 1.7.50
      * sqlite >= 3.6.19
      * taglib >= 1.9.0
      * expat
      * cmake 3.2.0

   2. Install optional dependencies:

      * dbus 1.0.x (optional)
      * flac
      * mad
      * vorbis
      * ogg
      * opus
      * faad2
      * pulse

   3. Run cmake:

      > cmake [options] .

      Options:

        -DWITH_DBUS=False               - Build without DBUS support
        -DWITH_NLS=False                - Build without Native Language Support
        -DWITH_OPENGL=False             - Build without OpenGL Support
        -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=prefix   - Set installation prefix. Default is /usr
        -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=type         - Set the build type. Available types: Release, Debug, RelWithDebInfo and MinSizeRel (default).
        -DCMAKE_INSTALL_LIBDIR=lib      - Set the name of the directory where libraries are installed (typically lib / lib32 / lib64). Default is lib.

   4. Compile

      > make

   5. Install

      > sudo make install

   6. Run the software

      > gogglesmm
